title: Get 1 Month Off This Huge 4 Beds/3 Baths Apartment
posting_body: ['One Free Month!', 'KEY NOTES:', 'Rent Controlled', 'Rent: $6295', 'Deposit: $3000 on approved credit', 'Pets: Cats', '*Pictures shown are an example*', 'Discovery the essence of luxury', 'Genuine, luxuriously tranquil and spaciously designed.', '14th', 'Ave. combines modernized living in a traditional city environment.', 'Positioned in San Francisco’s Richmond District, 14th Ave. presents six uniquely renovated units located directly across San Francisco’s infamous Golden Gate Park.', 'With an impeccable arrangement minutes from the historic Park Presidio, 14th Ave Apartments have been reconditioned to enhance the comfortableness of urban living.', 'As one of San Francisco’s premier neighborhoods, 14th Ave the ideal setting to navigate the city.', '14th', 'Ave provides access to some of California’s most famous attractions including California Academy of Sciences, San Francisco’s Presidio, and three major universities in the city—University of San Francisco, University of California San Francisco, and San Francisco State University—are all within minutes away.', 'MUNI, Tech Buses, Bike Lanes and Trails, 82 Walk Score (Very Walkable), 96 Bike Score (Biker’s Paradise, 76 Ride Score (Excellent Transit)', '14th', 'Ave. presents an arrangement of six remarkably sizable units, expanding 1,600 sq.', 'ft., including four bedrooms and three bathrooms.', 'Open and comfortable design delivers the space necessary to build your future in such a crowded city.', 'With beautifully crafted Chef’s Kitchen and high-end appliances, fulfilling your culinary interests will always be a breeze.', 'Each of the elegantly designed units includes granite counter tops, custom stainless steel fixtures and an abundance of cabinet space.', '14th', 'Ave. is part of an elite group of luxury apartment apartments that offer 1600 sq.', 'ft. units.']
